data.title: Instant Quotes On Private Jet Shared Flights
data.meta_description: With a Dedicated Fleet of over 350 jets and over 2,100+ aircraft in the XO Alliance Fleet, quickly find the perfect private jet charter for your destination.
data.text: The XO brand is comprised of a portfolio of companies, including XO Global LLC, XO Assets LLC, and Apollo Jets, LLC. XO Global LLC, an air charter broker, is not a direct air carrier and does not own or operate any aircraft. All flights will be operated by properly licensed U.S. or foreign air carriers. XO Assets LLC and its sister companies beneficially own or lease the Vista Members' fleet. All services are subject to the terms and conditions available at www.flyxo.com/legal. Fla. Seller of Travel Ref. No. ST42114.
